title: We Are Olympians Final
description:
America's greatest athletes are returning home...and they need jobs.

Starring Sasheer Zamata, Michael Hartney, and Amber Nelson
Written by Matt Starr
Directed by Justin Tyler
Filmed and Edited by Matt Starr

Originally performed live on Maude Night at The Upright Citizens Brigade Theatre in New York City on August 13, 2012.
